long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
🚀 Effortlessly export Trustpilot reviews from the listing detail page to a XLS/CSV file.

🔧 How it Works:
1️⃣ Open an Trustpilot listing detail page.
2️⃣ Click open our extension, then click the Export button.
3️⃣ Done! Sit back and just wait a moment, let our extension handle the rest.

🔥 Key Features:
1️⃣ Run in the background without waiting for finish.
2️⃣ Export on multiple listing detail pages simultaneous.
3️⃣ Export reviews for current item to a xls/csv file, data include: User Name, User Country, User Is Verified, User Experienced Date, Review Published Date, Language, Likes, Rating, Review Title, Review Text, Origin Search Url.

🎯 Targeted Users: business owners, data analysts, and competitor researchers alike.

💡 Benefit from our dedicated support team! We're here to assist you at every step and provide prompt, knowledgeable help.

💪 Take control of your business data management and make informed decisions with Trustpilot  Review Exporter today!

Note: This extension is an independent creation and is not affiliated with or endorsed by Trustpilot ❗️🔒
